parameters.name: query
parameters.value: SELECT ( COUNT(*) as ?count)   WHERE {       GRAPH ?g     {         ?s ?p ?o. FILTER (regex(str(?s), "bugzilla")).     } }

parameters.name: query
parameters.value: SELECT ( COUNT(*) as ?count)  WHERE {     GRAPH ?g     {         ?s ?p ?o. FILTER (regex(str(?s), "simulink")).     } }

parameters.name: query
parameters.value: SELECT (count(*) as ?count)   WHERE {      GRAPH ?g     {           ?s ?p ?o.   FILTER (contains(str(?g), "bugzilla") ).       } }   LIMIT 25

parameters.name: query
parameters.value: SELECT (count(*) as ?count)   WHERE {      GRAPH ?g     {           ?s ?p ?o.   FILTER (contains(str(?g), "simulink") ).       } }   LIMIT 25

resources.name: number of non bugz and sim trips(stardog)

parameters.name: query
parameters.value: SELECT ( COUNT(DISTINCT *) as ?count)  WHERE {     GRAPH ?g     {         ?s ?p ?o. FILTER (!regex(str(?s), "simulink") || !regex(str(?s), "bugzilla") ).     } }

parameters.name: query
parameters.value: SELECT (count(*)as ?count)  WHERE {  GRAPH ?g     {           ?s ?p ?o.   }{ SELECT ?g  WHERE {      GRAPH ?g     {           ?s ?p ?o.        FILTER (contains(str(?s), "rm-services") ).       } }}}

parameters.name: query
parameters.value: SELECT * WHERE {  GRAPH ?g     {           ?s ?p ?o.   }{ SELECT ?g  WHERE {      GRAPH ?g     {           ?s ?p ?o.        FILTER (contains(str(?s), "rm-services") ).       } }}}

parameters.name: query
parameters.value: PREFIX  oslc_rm:    <http://open-services.net/ns/rm#>   select ?implemented_req where  { FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?implemented_req oslc_rm:validatedBy ?test_case } { SELECT DISTINCT ?implemented_req   WHERE  {  GRAPH ?g    {  ?component ?implements ?implemented_req .FILTER (regex(str(?implements), "implements")) . }      } } }

parameters.name: query
parameters.value: PREFIX  oslc_rm:    <http://open-services.net/ns/rm#> PREFIX  oslc_am:    <http://open-services.net/ns/am#> PREFIX  oslc_cm:    <http://open-services.net/ns/cm#> select DISTINCT ?implemented_non_changed_req where  {   GRAPH ?g1      {     FILTER NOT EXISTS {       ?change_request oslc_cm:changes ?implemented_non_changed_req         }       GRAPH ?g3            {         ?component oslc_am:implements ?implemented_non_changed_req .       }    } }

parameters.name: query
parameters.value: PREFIX oslc_cm: <http://open-services.net/ns/cm#> PREFIX oslc_am: <http://open-services.net/ns/am#> SELECT DISTINCT ?s WHERE {   {     GRAPH ?g      {       ?s oslc_am:implements <http://git.md.kth.se:8081/pror/services/rm-services/ProR_Search_Spec.reqif/resources/requirements/REQ-25>     } .   }UNION {     GRAPH ?g1      {       ?s oslc_cm:changes <http://git.md.kth.se:8081/pror/services/rm-services/ProR_Search_Spec.reqif/resources/requirements/REQ-25>.     }    } }

parameters.name: query
parameters.value: PREFIX  oslc_cm:    <http://open-services.net/ns/cm#>   PREFIX  oslc_am:    <http://open-services.net/ns/am#>   PREFIX  oslc_rm:    <http://open-services.net/ns/rm#> select DISTINCT ?change_request where  {   GRAPH ?g   {     {       ?change_request oslc_cm:changes <http://git.md.kth.se:8081/pror/services/rm-services/ProR_Search_Spec.reqif/resources/requirements/REQ-25>          } UNION  {       ?change_request oslc_cm:changes ?refined_or_refining_req.         {           GRAPH ?g2 {             <http://git.md.kth.se:8081/pror/services/rm-services/ProR_Search_Spec.reqif/resources/requirements/REQ-25>               oslc_rm:refines ?refined_or_refining_req           }         } UNION {           GRAPH ?g1 {             ?refined_or_refining_req oslc_rm:refines <http://git.md.kth.se:8081/pror/services/rm-services/ProR_Search_Spec.reqif/resources/requirements/REQ-25>           }         }                      }     }   }

parameters.name: query
parameters.value: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX oslc_cm: <http://open-services.net/ns/cm#> PREFIX oslc_rm: <http://open-services.net/ns/rm#> SELECT ?element ?type WHERE {   GRAPH ?g1 {     FILTER NOT EXISTS {       ?change_request oslc_cm:changes ?element.     }     {         GRAPH ?g2 {           ?element rdf:type ?type.           FILTER (STRSTARTS(str(?type), "http://open-services.net/ns/rm#") ).         }              }     UNION     {         GRAPH ?g3 {           ?element rdf:type ?type.           FILTER (regex(str(?type), "simulink") ).         }     }   }  }

resources.name: SELECT representation of alll requirements resources

parameters.name: query
parameters.value: prefix rdf:    <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>  DESCRIBE ?s ?null_node  WHERE {   GRAPH ?g   {     ?s rdf:type ?rdf_type.     ?s ?p ?null_node.          FILTER regex(str(?rdf_type), "http://mathworks.com/simulink/r") .   } }

resources.name: SELECT representation of alll change requests (Copy)
SELECT representation of alll simulink blocks (Copy)

parameters.name: query
parameters.value: prefix rdf:    <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>  CONSTRUCT {   ?s ?p ?o.   ?null_node ?p_null_node ?o_null_node } WHERE {   GRAPH ?g   {     ?s rdf:type ?rdf_type.     ?s ?p ?null_node.     FILTER regex(str(?rdf_type), "http://mathworks.com/simulink/r") .   } }

parameters.name: query
parameters.value: PREFIX  oslc_rm:    <http://open-services.net/ns/rm#> PREFIX  oslc_am:    <http://open-services.net/ns/am#> PREFIX  oslc_cm:    <http://open-services.net/ns/cm#> select DISTINCT ?implemented_non_changed_req where  {   GRAPH ?g1      {     FILTER NOT EXISTS {       ?change_request oslc_cm:changes ?implemented_non_changed_req         }     SERVICE <http://localhost:8080/fuseki/simulink/query> {       GRAPH ?g3            {         ?component oslc_am:implements ?implemented_non_changed_req .       }     }     } }

parameters.name: query
parameters.value: PREFIX oslc_cm: <http://open-services.net/ns/cm#> PREFIX oslc_am: <http://open-services.net/ns/am#> SELECT DISTINCT ?s WHERE {   {     GRAPH ?g      {       ?s oslc_am:implements <http://git.md.kth.se:8081/pror/services/rm-services/ProR_Search_Spec.reqif/resources/requirements/REQ-25>     } .   }UNION {   SERVICE <http://localhost:8080/fuseki/Bugzilla/query> {     GRAPH ?g1      {       ?s oslc_cm:changes <http://git.md.kth.se:8081/pror/services/rm-services/ProR_Search_Spec.reqif/resources/requirements/REQ-25>.     }   }    } }

parameters.value: PREFIX  oslc_cm:    <http://open-services.net/ns/cm#>   PREFIX  oslc_am:    <http://open-services.net/ns/am#>   PREFIX  oslc_rm:    <http://open-services.net/ns/rm#> select DISTINCT ?change_request where  {   GRAPH ?g   {     {       ?change_request oslc_cm:changes <http://git.md.kth.se:8081/pror/services/rm-services/ProR_Search_Spec.reqif/resources/requirements/REQ-25>          } UNION  {       ?change_request oslc_cm:changes ?refined_or_refining_req.       SERVICE <http://localhost:8080/fuseki/ReqIf/query> {         {           GRAPH ?g2 {             <http://git.md.kth.se:8081/pror/services/rm-services/ProR_Search_Spec.reqif/resources/requirements/REQ-25>               oslc_rm:refines ?refined_or_refining_req           }         } UNION {           GRAPH ?g1 {             ?refined_or_refining_req oslc_rm:refines <http://git.md.kth.se:8081/pror/services/rm-services/ProR_Search_Spec.reqif/resources/requirements/REQ-25>           }         }             }          }     }   }

parameters.name: query
parameters.value: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX oslc_cm: <http://open-services.net/ns/cm#> PREFIX oslc_rm: <http://open-services.net/ns/rm#> SELECT ?element ?type WHERE {   GRAPH ?g1 {     FILTER NOT EXISTS {       ?change_request oslc_cm:changes ?element.     }     {       SERVICE <http://localhost:8080/fuseki/ReqIf/query> {         GRAPH ?g2 {           ?element rdf:type ?type.           FILTER (STRSTARTS(str(?type), "http://open-services.net/ns/rm#") ).         }                }     }     UNION     {       SERVICE <http://localhost:8080/fuseki/simulink/query> {         GRAPH ?g3 {           ?element rdf:type ?type.
